WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:04:12.268 --> 00:04:15.867
river and sea that I met on my way

00:04:16.868 --> 00:04:18.868
all come from this little fluid  

00:04:19.201 --> 00:04:20.734
they gather together 

00:04:20.734 --> 00:04:21.867
and become river

00:04:24.268 --> 00:04:25.634
final to sea

00:04:28.301 --> 00:04:31.667
where will it go in the end?

00:04:35.201 --> 00:04:38.334
this hill stream seems common

00:04:39.247 --> 00:04:39.915
but in fact

00:04:40.035 --> 00:04:44.300
it is the headstream of Duliu River

00:04:45.501 --> 00:04:47.634
Duliu River sets off here

00:04:47.768 --> 00:04:48.932
passing Liuzhou in Guangxi Province

00:04:49.259 --> 00:04:51.909
rolls to Pearl River Delta Region

00:04:53.824 --> 00:04:57.311
when rain above Miaoling meets fog over forest in valley

00:04:58.052 --> 00:05:00.052
it turns into countless little fluids

00:05:00.607 --> 00:05:05.267
they flow along hills and take in other fluids

00:05:14.064 --> 00:05:16.200
through hundreds of thousands of villages and fields

00:05:16.526 --> 00:05:19.800
they finally turn into big river on which ships can travel

00:05:24.200 --> 00:05:26.299
it is fair to say what makes out Duliu River 

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:28.545
is rain and fog over Guizhou

00:05:29.200 --> 00:05:31.700
as well as Miaoling lay in the southeast of Guizhou Province

00:05:34.501 --> 00:05:35.300
at mention of Miaoling

00:05:35.531 --> 00:05:38.739
it is not one mountain 

00:05:41.471 --> 00:05:43.167
instead，from Huishui County in Qiannan 

00:05:43.167 --> 00:05:44.900
to Leishan County in Qiandongnan

00:05:45.268 --> 00:05:49.200
stretching mountains are everywhere from west to east

00:05:49.749 --> 00:05:51.749
it's called Miaoling

00:05:52.211 --> 00:05:55.047
because Miao and Dong people live at the zone

00:06:05.274 --> 00:06:07.274
in the following journey

00:06:08.095 --> 00:06:10.157
centered around Rongjiang County of Qiandongnan

00:06:10.341 --> 00:06:12.837
I visited several villages in east region of Miaoling

00:06:20.154 --> 00:06:22.928
I didn't visit any famous tourist attractions

00:06:22.928 --> 00:06:25.920
as Qianhu Miaozhai or Zhaoxing Dongzhai

00:06:26.459 --> 00:06:31.556
but nature villages scattered over the mountains instead

00:06:35.448 --> 00:06:37.034
Zengying Village is a big Dong village

00:06:38.359 --> 00:06:43.084
I expected to see people singing Dong songs over night here

00:06:43.722 --> 00:06:45.010
but when I got into the village

00:06:45.010 --> 00:06:47.567
I found out the village has no intention for tourist development yet

00:07:18.001 --> 00:07:20.001
Wind-rain Bridge is the signal of Dong village

00:07:20.432 --> 00:07:22.215
and a shelter for pedestrians

00:07:23.835 --> 00:07:26.267
while Drum Tower, for my understanding

00:07:27.068 --> 00:07:30.000
acts as the political and cultural center for a village

00:07:31.099 --> 00:07:33.099
they are the shiniest cultural signal for Dong people 

00:07:34.707 --> 00:07:36.707
and might become the most likely protected culture heritage

00:07:37.789 --> 00:07:39.789
during urbanization construction 

00:08:06.001 --> 00:08:10.076
a grandpa told me how busy drum tower was in old days

00:08:11.096 --> 00:08:13.715
but when it comes to the age of  labor service export

00:08:13.715 --> 00:08:15.715
young people run out mountains 

00:08:15.991 --> 00:08:19.756
those singing boys stay behind still

00:08:31.501 --> 00:08:35.390
it feels like that we no longer write letters

00:08:35.839 --> 00:08:37.560
wind-rain bridges and drum towers

00:08:37.713 --> 00:08:40.144
were replaced by current phones and pads

00:09:00.754 --> 00:09:03.807
I run into a county leader back town that day

00:09:05.539 --> 00:09:07.539
though the communication sounded a bit serious

00:09:07.908 --> 00:09:09.382
when he spoke of the village of his birth

00:09:09.844 --> 00:09:12.434
Mr Pan knew every detail of it

00:09:13.483 --> 00:09:15.483
what's the main income here?

00:09:16.193 --> 00:09:18.193
labor export

00:09:18.531 --> 00:09:20.376
what about agriculture？

00:09:20.529 --> 00:09:21.029
rice

00:09:24.416 --> 00:09:26.416
it seems...young people

00:09:26.901 --> 00:09:29.427
don't wear national dresses any more

00:09:29.829 --> 00:09:30.329
no

00:09:38.021 --> 00:09:39.067
this is the traditional clothes

00:09:39.067 --> 00:09:40.467
but pants are not

00:09:49.454 --> 00:09:51.702
all of these may disappear  slowly

00:09:54.704 --> 00:09:57.416
Zengying Village lives at its own pace

00:09:57.817 --> 00:09:59.817
away from the great tourist development wave

00:10:05.296 --> 00:10:08.690
traditions are not maintained or deduced on purpose

00:10:10.401 --> 00:10:11.224
maybe in future

00:10:11.377 --> 00:10:12.972
traditional  wooden houses

00:10:12.972 --> 00:10:15.220
 would be replaced by brick and cement dwellings

00:10:16.735 --> 00:10:18.735
however it think it fair and nature

00:10:19.290 --> 00:10:22.808
everyone has the rights to pursue a better life

00:10:41.521 --> 00:10:43.986
if it's said the change of social communication

00:10:43.986 --> 00:10:48.000
shakes Dong village 's culture foundation 

00:10:48.709 --> 00:10:51.917
then for Kongshen Miaozhai isolated in remote Miaoling

00:10:53.556 --> 00:10:55.030
with the help of social media

00:10:55.399 --> 00:10:58.545
it could better keep its traditions

00:11:02.333 --> 00:11:04.612
I'm going to

00:11:04.612 --> 00:11:07.500
a really remote village

00:11:07.694 --> 00:11:10.751
I know I describe a village remote every time I drive to 

00:11:10.751 --> 00:11:12.751
but this one is really really distant

00:11:13.523 --> 00:11:15.709
it takes more than 3 hrs

00:11:15.709 --> 00:11:17.554
start from Rongjiang County of Qiandongnan

00:11:17.800 --> 00:11:20.079
so...I'm driving quite long

00:11:20.479 --> 00:11:21.434
it's 1p.m. now

00:11:21.435 --> 00:11:24.364
I heard there's a festival in the village today

00:11:24.364 --> 00:11:26.364
called Maoren Festival

00:11:27.074 --> 00:11:28.640
villagers will dress up

00:11:29.735 --> 00:11:30.837
 the opportunity is too good to miss

00:11:30.838 --> 00:11:32.342
first for the festival

00:11:32.495 --> 00:11:37.100
second for  miniskirt, its unique dress for girls

00:13:46.612 --> 00:13:47.528
Excuse me

00:13:47.528 --> 00:13:49.731
Is Kongshen Village there?

00:13:52.808 --> 00:13:53.817
yes! this way!

00:13:54.217 --> 00:13:55.381
how is the way?

00:13:55.381 --> 00:13:56.996
as tough as the one before

00:14:29.063 --> 00:14:31.063
here I am! 

00:14:32.919 --> 00:14:34.919
The car park is full

00:14:38.014 --> 00:14:40.850
the ceremony has begun!

00:14:42.365 --> 00:14:43.188
let me take a look

00:14:44.982 --> 00:14:46.053
it's up there

00:14:46.360 --> 00:14:49.165
they are celebrating a traditional festival

00:15:10.406 --> 00:15:16.680
Lusheng dance of Miao People

00:15:20.301 --> 00:15:23.354
Kongshen Miaozhai lay in a rural valley in Miaoling

00:15:23.847 --> 00:15:26.413
it is one of the branches of Miao People, called Jinji Miao

00:15:26.988 --> 00:15:30.196
or Duanqun Miao in more grounded term

00:15:51.714 --> 00:15:54.642
miniskirt is common dress feature for Duanqun Miao

00:15:54.789 --> 00:15:59.793
while Maoren Festival is unique in Liangwang Town

00:16:00.193 --> 00:16:01.667
the festival was ancient from old rules

00:16:01.667 --> 00:16:04.837
that relatives could not marry each other 

00:16:04.837 --> 00:16:07.629
in the war era

00:16:08.386 --> 00:16:09.983
time flows to the peace era

00:16:09.983 --> 00:16:13.642
and it drifted into the local Valentine's Day

00:16:14.193 --> 00:16:16.008
when it comes to the rural tourism era

00:16:16.439 --> 00:16:17.851
miniskirt and Maoren Festival

00:16:18.158 --> 00:16:21.056
act as cultural signals for Kongshen Village going out the mountain

00:16:31.215 --> 00:16:33.215
to my surprise

00:16:33.215 --> 00:16:35.418
expect me as an individual tourist

00:16:35.828 --> 00:16:39.098
ournalists and photographers were invited by county governor 

00:16:40.489 --> 00:16:42.000
brought  miniskirt and Maoren Festival

00:16:42.239 --> 00:16:44.858
communicative and cultural function

00:17:15.138 --> 00:17:17.138
besides own team

00:17:18.220 --> 00:17:20.994
the county also invited other towns and villages to perform

00:17:28.750 --> 00:17:30.000
here is the Nangong Village from Taijiang Town

00:17:30.235 --> 00:17:31.894
final attack is coming!

00:17:55.819 --> 00:17:59.182
to be honest, the performance is lack of appreciation

00:18:00.697 --> 00:18:03.034
but it is the most valuable part of it

00:18:06.535 --> 00:18:08.039
people who joined the show

00:18:08.564 --> 00:18:10.750
were not professionals recruited

00:18:11.046 --> 00:18:13.201
but local citizens

00:18:14.468 --> 00:18:16.468
they wore own costumes

00:18:16.469 --> 00:18:18.159
and danced accustomed step

00:18:18.776 --> 00:18:23.129
every smile and movement comes out of nature 

00:18:26.622 --> 00:18:31.781
they didnt come with  ambition to guard traditional culture

00:18:31.782 --> 00:18:34.154
but the happiness of singing and dancing

00:18:34.368 --> 00:18:36.368
besides, the country treated them dinner

00:18:45.756 --> 00:18:47.291
when people was busy on the hill

00:18:47.599 --> 00:18:49.599
chefs were busy with dinner 

00:19:02.495 --> 00:19:05.176
local performance teams 

00:19:05.484 --> 00:19:07.887
journalists and photographers were invited to the village feast

00:19:50.421 --> 00:19:51.523
it was Saturday

00:19:52.047 --> 00:19:54.047
and the feast was arranged on the playground of village school

00:19:55.284 --> 00:19:56.510
Kongshen Elementary School

00:19:56.510 --> 00:20:00.138
is the biggest and flattest place in the village

00:20:07.501 --> 00:20:09.501
this table were all young people 

00:20:10.118 --> 00:20:12.861
the four girls were well dressed 

00:20:15.213 --> 00:20:16.717
I think...

00:20:16.717 --> 00:20:21.150
you need to get close to learn about the culture

00:20:24.612 --> 00:20:27.293
can you send the pictures to me later?

00:20:27.508 --> 00:20:28.331
sure!

00:20:38.564 --> 00:20:40.564
you are all very pretty!

00:20:40.565 --> 00:20:43.432
could you introduce about the festival?

00:20:44.301 --> 00:20:47.261
married people... meet their old lovers...

00:20:48.001 --> 00:20:50.001
hahahahhahahha

00:20:50.002 --> 00:20:52.134
but we are all signals!

00:20:53.435 --> 00:20:54.723
people sing love songs to each other

00:20:55.185 --> 00:20:57.928
get dressed up

00:20:58.731 --> 00:21:00.000
kind like blind dates

00:21:01.441 --> 00:21:03.441
is it like Valentine's Day?

00:21:04.089 --> 00:21:05.717
Yes! Miao People's Valentine's Day!

00:21:05.717 --> 00:21:07.717
so are you coming back to village for blind dates?

00:21:08.179 --> 00:21:09.312
yes!

00:21:29.469 --> 00:21:31.841
there was a camp fire and performance planned after feast 

00:21:32.737 --> 00:21:34.737
which should be my most anticipated moment

00:21:36.345 --> 00:21:41.783
but a heavy rain fell suddenly before the feast

00:22:12.131 --> 00:22:14.131
it rained for half an hour

00:22:14.810 --> 00:22:17.615
people squeezed in the school

00:22:19.874 --> 00:22:22.741
the following activities had to be canceled 

00:22:29.181 --> 00:22:31.924
it's 7 p.m. now

00:22:32.325 --> 00:22:35.254
rain gets heavier and heavier

00:22:37.017 --> 00:22:38.534
and it's getting dark

00:22:38.798 --> 00:22:41.696
now I finally run into my car

00:22:42.747 --> 00:22:43.446
it's getting cold

00:22:43.816 --> 00:22:47.426
the temperature drops immediately after rain

00:22:48.725 --> 00:22:49.889
my car keeps me warm

00:22:51.714 --> 00:22:53.590
I haven't eaten anything yet today

00:22:53.590 --> 00:22:55.663
all day I'm busy shooting

00:22:59.689 --> 00:23:01.689
if I went for eating

00:23:02.244 --> 00:23:04.244
then good shots would be missed

00:23:07.679 --> 00:23:09.679
I assume rain would stop after an hour

00:23:11.194 --> 00:23:13.597
before that, I have to wait in the car

00:23:21.879 --> 00:23:23.879
when I came back to the school

00:23:24.635 --> 00:23:26.635
tables were moved into classrooms

00:23:27.314 --> 00:23:28.385
crowds dispersed

00:23:28.878 --> 00:23:31.002
I eventually forgot to send girls their photos

00:23:55.334 --> 00:23:58.361
 weather is changeable in Guizhou

00:23:59.381 --> 00:24:01.846
it starts to rain now... you see

00:24:03.299 --> 00:24:05.299
people all run away

00:24:38.140 --> 00:24:40.140
culture of Kongshen Village are eager to walk out

00:24:40.355 --> 00:24:43.687
tradition heritage is more difficult than construction maintenance

00:24:45.852 --> 00:24:47.821
whether to inherit traditional  culture or develop the economy

00:24:47.821 --> 00:24:49.529
both need money

00:24:50.049 --> 00:24:53.288
still I feel luck to meet you right now

00:25:00.625 --> 00:25:02.625
Maolan is my last stop in Guizhou

00:25:03.521 --> 00:25:06.233
and my favorite place in Guizhou

00:25:08.151 --> 00:25:11.297
Libo gives all fame to Little Qikong and Zhangjiang

00:25:11.852 --> 00:25:15.741
leaving Maolan peace and undisturbed

00:25:17.435 --> 00:25:19.435
I left all my tiredness and keen 

00:25:19.435 --> 00:25:22.072
in this invisible forest

00:25:22.839 --> 00:25:23.755
for Guizhou

00:25:24.589 --> 00:25:27.859
What else would you tell us?

